author_ssm: Rachel Pedderson and Rhyannon J. Rodriguez, 2012.
abstract_ssm: Parasite was an artist-run organization, primarily active between the years 1997 to 1998, that was committed to supporting, documenting, and presenting project-based artwork. The Archive includes administrative records, articles, books, correspondence, ephemera, photography, promotional materials, objects, and audiovisual elements.
